name: Dystopian Hours II- Loneliness
description: Taking place in Monte Amiata, this second scene seems more serene, but if you look closely, it’s full of sorrow. The good old times are now gone and you’re left alone with some vague memories and the regret that you didn’t appreciate how lucky you were at the time. Now it’s all gone and you’re down a dark path which you don’t know where it leads. Once you pass through the door, will it be the end of your story or a completely new beginning?
